query:
WITH ranked AS (
  SELECT id, name, totalSales,
         ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY totalSales DESC, name ASC) as rank_num
  FROM services
  WHERE active = 1
)
SELECT * FROM ranked WHERE rank_num > 20 ORDER BY name ASC LIMIT 10
